title: 请问怎么查看MM的报错问题
author: 颅内开灯
txt_content:
本帖最后由 XieLaoDD 于 2020-6-18 11:29 编辑 

我MM一直在疯狂报错刷logs
[10:39:16 ERROR]:[MythicMobs] AN EXCEPTION HAS OCCURED:
[10:39:16 ERROR]: [MythicMobs]     null (java.lang.NullPointerException)
[10:39:16 ERROR]: [MythicMobs] This error has been saved in the Error Logs folder

然后logs的内容是
java.lang.NullPointerException
MythicMobs version: 4.3.2-SNAPSHOT
Bukkit version: git-Spigot-dcd1643-e60fc34 (MC: 1.12.2)

请问这种情况怎么处理呢
我记得MM是不是有一个Debug模式来着
问题解决了：世界卸载了,怪物还在

replies.author: 南柯郡守
replies.txt_content: 可以试试更新下mm的版本
